name: VOXELFINE #8: "Skull of a Skeleton with Burning Cigarette" by Vincent Van Gogh 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: I wanted to do a Van Gogh, but not something well-known. This painting is right up my alley given the macabre theme, but I also just wanted to make a voxel skellie. The smoke was fun, too. Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
